<i>adverb</i>: 간명히 [간명히], 간략히 [갈랴키] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>간명히 [간명히]</dt><br>
<dd>concisely</dd><br>
<dd>간단하고 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Clearly and simply.</dd><br>
<dt>간략히 [갈랴키]</dt><br>
<dd>briefly; concisely</dd><br>
<dd>간단하고 짤막하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Simply and briefly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>